column6: aria-label attribute does not exist or is empty--aria-labelledby attribute does not exist- references elements that do not exist or references elements that are empty--Form element does not have an implicit (wrapped) <label>--Form element does not have an explicit <label>--Element has no title attribute or the title attribute is empty--Element's default semantics were not overridden with role="none"--Element's default semantics were not overridden with role="presentation"
